Aug 12 2023, Pretoria

Looks like I needed to add the following to _quarto.yml to get the .xml files generated

listing:
  contents: posts
  sort: "date desc"
  type: default
  categories: true
  sort-ui: false
  feed: true

See https://community.rstudio.com/t/setting-up-rss-feed-for-a-category-in-quarto-blog/146489/3

